livecd-rootfs (2.257) utopic; urgency=medium

  * Drop the click packages moved in 2.255 from the rootfs, leaving them
    only in the custom tarball.

 -- Colin Watson <cjwatson@ubuntu.com>  Wed, 15 Oct 2014 21:07:38 +0100

